-- 
Alhokair to Open Naartjie Stores in Middle East, Times Reports

-- B y   R o b e r t   B r a n d
-- 
2011-08-21T07:31:22Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-08-21/alhokair-to-open-naartjie-stores-in-middle-east-times-reports.html
Fawaz Abdulaziz Alhokair & Co. (ALHOKAIR) 
signed an agreement to sell clothes by Naartjie Custom Kids Inc.
in the  Middle East  and North Africa, the Johannesburg-based
 Sunday Times  reported, citing Naartjie Chief Executive Joe
Franceschi.  Riyadh-based Alhokair has opened seven Naartjie outlets in
Saudi Arabia and plans 50 more stores in the Middle East and
North Africa, Franceschi said, according to the newspaper.
Naartjie, founded in South Africa 22 years ago, also plans to
open stores in India, China and Brazil, the Sunday Times said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
